Setup: 

Open Cpp.ino with arduino IDE
(on first boot): 
-> Setup arduino IDE to ESP32 freenove = https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Freenove/Freenove_Ultimate_Starter_Kit_for_ESP32/master/C/C_Tutorial.pdf
-> Add libraries from lib folder to arduino IDE (sketch -> Include library -> add ZIP library)
-> Setup SERVER_URI to the API server endpoint.
-> Flash firmware.

Setup device:
-> Join device network. (password: H3LL0FR0MSL1M1IMaTesTAnDWILLB3ChanG3d)
-> go to 192.168.4.1 (general access network IP) 
-> Enter WIFI SSID & password.
-> Enter enter API key 

